title: 2 bedrooms in-law units, GREAT neighborhood!!
posting_body: ['A cozy two bedrooms, one bath in-law unit with separate entrance.', 'READY TO MOVE IN ON SEPTEMBER 1ST!', 'Features:', '**Refrigerator, new stove and kitchen hood provided.', '**Energy saving heating system for both air conditioning and heating.', '**Laundry on site.', 'Located in a nice and convenient Westborough neighborhood in South San Francisco.', 'Easy access to 280 freeway.', '2 miles to South San Francisco Bart.', 'Walking distance to Westborough Park.', 'Close to Safeway, Philz Coffee, Seafood City, Marina Market, Walgreen, Skyline college, Chase Bank, and more….', 'Rent is $2450 per month, deposit $1000', 'Garbage included.', 'Water and PGE are not included.', 'Street parking only', 'Credit check $40 for application, refund from first month’s rent after lease is signed.', 'Minimum one-year lease.', 'Pets and smoking prohibited.', 'Please text for more information or appointment.']
